summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing construction of the West Seattle Alki, Sewer Separation, Contract No. 4 for the separation of existing combined sewers in the area bounded generally by Duwamish Head on the north, Elliott Bay on the east, Southwest Admiral Way and Southwest Hanford Street on the south and Puget Sound on the west and making an appropriation from the Sewer Improvement Fund therefor.
